        public void saveIndicesPreferences(int[] indices)
        Call saveIndicesPreferences(int[]) to store/update the indices of player. int[0] is book index. int[1] is lesson index. int[2] is item index. int[3] is sentence index.
        Parameters:
        indices - an array of int consists of four indices {book, lesson, item, sentence}
